Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打从心里大叫一句\N好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信总有一天\N一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你不会忘记最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰教练明天就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写贺词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贺词?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天三鹰教练\N就要结婚了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家要在网球拍上\N各写一句贺词送给他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位要不要写?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,那由管理员先写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N你应该有话想跟教练说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写什么好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写一句怨恨他的话也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说,你居然把我甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就不能诚心诚意\N为别人的幸福感到高兴呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(祝你永远幸福音无响子)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#95 啊～感动!\N包含于戒指中的奶奶之爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,让我们暗地里\N祝福三鹰的婚姻幸福美满
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说喜宴在皇家饭店举行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想吃吃看\N一流饭店的法国料理的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说蜜月旅行是从希腊到西班牙\N环绕爱琴海一周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员放弃他还真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么因缘\N怎么会选到这个人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,管理员呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在准备料理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且吃管理员的拿手好菜\N忍耐一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃的话\N不吃也不要紧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的耳朵什么都听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是五代\N你们进展到什么地步了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个…这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问订婚或结婚的日子\N你们多少应该有谈一下吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,还没有谈到那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,管理员的爸妈\N已经答应了不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来轮到五代带管理员\N去见你爸妈才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很没用耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话\N说不定管理员会变心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想把菜端过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那个…\N-什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…最近去一趟新泻好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能正式去见\N我爸妈还有奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在马上去打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,裕作\N你干得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,所以最近我想请个假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样,打铁要趁热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我奶奶老是擅作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,不一定非得明天去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也有你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟迟早都得要去拜访的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你慢吞吞的\N所以我们才下楼来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,这样很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,等这个春天等得真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲定了,今晚为了庆祝\N他们两人要去新泻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛快快喝一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妆会不会太浓了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服不会太花俏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说穿这一套比较好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你们看家罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我向奶奶问好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员不要紧吧\N她好像蛮紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪,年纪比五代大\N而且又是再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代本人是无所谓\N不过,他爸妈会答应吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟乡下人对这种事比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把朱美带回家去\N他爸妈才会大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸妈\N知道我全部的事情吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如我的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我是…第二次结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心,你一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是奶奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,五代他们已经出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会啊,当然会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,再见罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁打来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(汤之町车站)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪\N奶奶应该会来接我们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你这是干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你看起来好有精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对,应该是我们家的响子\N欢迎你来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家就快到了哦,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是裕作出生长大的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,别客气,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公\N裕作,裕作回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为什么还开门做生意?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得响子专程来看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好,一路上辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面,我是音无响子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么我回来啦\N这么重大的日子还开门做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来也是打算\N休息一天等你们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是奶奶坚持\N一定要开店做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,为什么要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正响子\N要嫁到我们家做媳妇了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又何必跟她那么见外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-对不对?\N-是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思没什么好招待的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪排饭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好,欢迎你来我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两客炸虾饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我到店里帮忙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这怎么可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系,让她去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧\N身体动一动也比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她去忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很重要的事要跟你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么重要的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你有结婚资金吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然问这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有还是没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚找到工作而已\N接下来会慢慢存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让响子等到\N你存够钱为止吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这是奶奶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管,拿去用就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你存够钱娶老婆\N我得活到一百岁才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是给我这么大一笔钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要给你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我存起来要当棺材本的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我死之前要还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会给你办一个\N非常风光的葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能说点中听的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们请了新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是,她是裕作未来的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,真是个大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也省得去跟街坊邻居介绍\N真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,还是奶奶聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸天妇罗饭和南蛮咖哩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,炸天妇罗饭和南蛮咖哩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很闲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊\N我回来不是为了做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来看你的孙媳妇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是裕作的新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的,简直像个洋娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上我请客\N大家别客气尽管吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了,小裕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是好福气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,裕作,还有一个外送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是三丁目的村野家\N两碗天妇罗荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托,你们也关心一下响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是顺着奶奶的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟不晓得她老人家\N什么时候会走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又说这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个孙媳妇\N真是又贤慧又美丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本日已打烊)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟奶奶到二楼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里我来整理\N裕作,你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我年轻时\N爷爷送给我的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不值钱,这个给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奶奶最珍贵的纪念品\N不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可以收下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到别的地方去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话,走开啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戒指啊,我早就决定\N要送给裕作的新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当作是我的遗物\N收下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你怎么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作是我亲手带大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他很迷糊,又靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是我全心栽培的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要好好照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要请他多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,你愿意收下这个戒指罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,谢谢奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦,一下子赶我出去\N一下子又叫我进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦,坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个戒指\N戴在响子的手指上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戒指哪来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,总算完成了一桩心事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你醒一醒啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在抱到曾孙之前\N我怎么可以死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没丧葬费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个满脸皱纹的臭奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好窝心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,您太夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你找到了一个好老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个不成材的儿子,今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于比较像样点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都来这么久了,你们还在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要好好的来\N提前庆祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,难得裕作带新娘子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做点小菜来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来\N-谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请\N-谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢哦,到底在搞什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人来了\N裕作,你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,帮我们开门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝喜事当然人多才热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝个痛快,喝个过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说裕作一直受到你们照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能住在他隔壁房\N也算是一种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,伯父,多喝一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来,管理员和五代\N你们要笑一笑,笑得开心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你们充满希望的未来\N整晚来喝赏雪酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样跟在一刻馆有什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,酒在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,响子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,祝你17岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奶奶送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,几乎都没看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,擅自进来你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这个房间很单调吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N你一直住在这个房间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,一直到高中毕业\N搬去一刻馆为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和橄榄球社的人一起照的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是惨败的时候照的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是看起来真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都看着\N这个城镇的风景生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,原来你们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么随便跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来看\N你们在做什么好事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么好事?我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,庆祝他们两人的婚事\N喝个痛快吧,喝个过瘾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,裕作,你也喝你也喝…
