Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有了结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N祝五代和管理员幸福美满
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也祝全国的相聚一刻影迷健康
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“只要这份爱还在!\N永远的一刻馆!”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.13,0:24:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.07,0:24:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻也是…woo
